urement on page 205, 207, 210 and 214; total release on page 449. {{dead link|date=April 2017|bot=medic}}{{cbignore|bot=medic}}</ref>\n|}   \n   \n{| class=\"wikitable\"   \n|-   \n!Report date   \n!Place   \n!Period  \n!Amount<br />(TBq)   \n!Source   \n|-   \n|12 April 2011   \n|Chernobyl   \n|25 April \u2013 June 1986   \n|align=right| 5,200,000\n|NISA<ref name=\"nisa-ines-2011-04-12\" />   \n|-   \n|12 April 2011   \n|Fukushima   \n|11 March \u2013 5 April 2011   \n|align=right| 630,000\n|NSC<ref name=\"jaif_64\" /><ref name=\"nisa-ines-2011-04-12\" />   \n|-   \n|12 April 2011   \n|Fukushima   \n|11 \u2013 17 March 2011   \n|align=right| 370,000\n|NISA<ref name=\"nisa-ines-2011-04-12\" />   \n|-   \n|April 2011   \n|Fukushima   \n|4 April 2011   \n|align=right| 154   \n|NSC<ref name=\"jaif_64\" />   \n|-   \n|25 April 2011   \n|Fukushima   \n|24 April 2011   \n|align=right| 24   \n|NSC<ref name=\"jaif_64\" />   \n|-   \n|6\u20137 June 2011   \n|Fukushima   \n|11 \u2013 17 March 2011   \n|align=right| 770,000\n|NISA<ref name=\"nhk-06_33\">{{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110409182124/http://www3.nhk.or.jp/daily/english/06_33.html |date=9 April 2011 }}. NHK, 6 June 2011, archived from [http://www3.nhk.or.jp/daily/english/06_33.html Original], retrieved on 6 June 2011.</ref>><ref name=\"nisa-2011-06-07a\" />\n|-   \n|7 June 2011   \n|Fukushima   \n|11 \u2013 17 March 2011   \n|align=right| 840,000\n|NISA,<ref name=\"nisa-2011-06-07b\">{{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120404084554/http://www.kantei.go.jp/foreign/kan/topics/201106/pdf/attach_04_2.pdf |date=4 April 2012 }}. NISA/Kantei, 7 June 2011, archived from [http://www.kantei.go.jp/foreign/kan/topics/201106/pdf/attach_04_2.pdf Original], retrieved on 14 June 2011.</ref> press printing<ref name=\"nhk-06_33\" />\n|-   \n|17 August 2011   \n|Fukushima   \n|3\u201316 August 2011   \n|align=right| 0.07   \n|Government<ref name=\"jaif_177\">{{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120130193819/http://www.jaif.or.jp/english/news_images/pdf/ENGNEWS01_1313640580P.pdf |date=30 January 2012 }}. JAIF / NHK, 18 August 2011, archived from [http://www.jaif.or.jp/english/news_images/pdf/ENGNEWS01_1313640580P.pdf Original], retrieved on 21 August 2011. Converted from 200 MBq/h in a two-week period.</ref>\n|-   \n|23 August 2011   \n|Fukushima   \n|12 March - 5 April 2011   \n|align=right| 630,000\n|NISA<ref name=\"jaif_182\">[https://web.archive.org/web/20140715063053/http://www.webcitation.org/61M8FBU3F ''Earthquake Report \u2013 JAIF, No. 182'']. JAIF / NHK, 23 August 2011, archived from [http://www.jaif.or.jp/english/news_images/pdf/ENGNEWS01_1314074607P.pdf Original] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111114110137/http://www.jaif.or.jp/english/news_images/pdf/ENGNEWS01_1314074607P.pdf |date=2011-11-14 }}, retrieved on 31 August 2011.</ref>\n|}\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n!rowspan=2| Report date\n!rowspan=2| Period\n!colspan=2| Into the sea<br />(TBq)\n!rowspan=2| Source\n|-\n!direct\n!indirect\n|-\n|21 May 2011\n|1 \u2013 6 April 2011\n|align=right| 4,700\n|\n|Tepco<ref name=\"tepco-110521e6\">{{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110526025819/http://www.tepco.co.jp/en/press/corp-com/release/betu11_e/images/110521e6.pdf |date=26 May 2011 }}. Tepco, 21 May 2011, archived from [http://www.tepco.co.jp/en/press/corp-com/release/betu11_e/images/110521e6.pdf Original], retrieved on 23 May 2011.</ref>\n|-\n|End of August 2011\n|March \u2013 August 2011\n|align=right| 3,500\n|align=right| 16,000\n|[[Japan Meteorological Agency|JMA]]<ref name=\"dradio-meereskontamination\">Dagmar R\u00f6hrlich: {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111104160520/http://www.dradio.de/dlf/sendungen/forschak/1547043/ |date=4 November 2011 }}{{in lang|de}}. In: ''dradio.de, Forschung Aktuell''. Deutschlandfunk, 5 September 2011, archived from [http://www.dradio.de/dlf/sendungen/forschak/1547043/ Original], retrieved on 7 September 2011; 1&nbsp;000 0